ygData.subject: Re: [EverQuest] Re: leveling
ygData.msgSnippet: Been awhile since I ve been to HK, but I believe you can take the rivervale book in the plane of knowledge, then head to Kithkor Forest, then follow the wall
ygData.messageBody:
Been awhile since I've been to HK, but I believe you
can take the rivervale book in the plane of knowledge,
then head to Kithkor Forest, then follow the wall to
zone into either the pass or keep, forget which one
comes first. (careful in Kithkor)
